BADGES:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/Java-21-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=openjdk)
![Spring Boot](https://img.shields.io/badge/Spring_Boot-3.x-brightgreen?style=for-the-badge&logo=springboot)
